quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  50,25,"“Jwakusiŵilila yambone, jwakusumba mpika, jwakaichila.”"
  50,26,"“Ajula juŵaŵisile nnungu jwine (jwakun’galagatila) pampepe ni Allah, basi mumponyani mu ilagasyo yawukali.”"
  50,27,"Ni tachiŵecheta n’jakwe jwangalekangana najo (jwachishetani): “Ambuje ŵetu! Une nganinansochelesya jwalakweju, nambo kuti jwaliji nkupotela kwakutalikangana nnope (ni yakuona).”"
  51,19,"Ni m’chipanje mwao mwaliji mwana liwunjili lyakumpa nkuŵenda ni nkwimidwa (ligongo lya kulisiŵilila kuŵenda)."
  51,20,"Ni petaka pana ilosyo (yakulosya ukombosi wa Allah) kwa ŵakusimichisya (chikulupi chao)."
  51,21,"Ni mu (kagumbidwe ka) jenumanja ŵakwe, ana ngankulola?"
  52,10,"Ni gachijenda matumbi ni kajende kaluŵilo."
  52,11,"Basi ipotesi lyele lisikulyo taachiipata ŵakanila."
  52,12,"Aŵala ŵaakuŵa nkung’anda mu yangali mate."
  53,4,"Nganigaŵa galakwego ikaŵeje maloŵe gakuuwula gagakuuwulidwa."
  53,5,"An’jiganyisye (Qur’anijo Jibulilu) jwamachili gamajinji."
  53,6,"Jwajukwete kaoneche kambone. Basi ni jwatamilichiche (pakaoneche kakwe kasyesyene kaŵan’guumbiile Allah)."